data.description:
This golf course home with a private pool could be yours! This 3-bed, 2-bath residence offers modern comfort. A 2-car garage and low-maintenance desert landscape frame the front porch.

Inside, a welcoming living room leads to a great room with vaulted ceilings, plantation shutters, wood-look and tile flooring, and backyard access. The kitchen features granite counters, stylish cabinets, a mosaic tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, a walk-in pantry, and a breakfast bar island. A versatile den adds flexibility.

The main bedroom includes plush carpeting, a walk-in closet, and an ensuite with dual sinks. Outdoors, enjoy a covered patio, a pool, and a stunning golf course view.

Don't miss out—make it yours today!
